reviewText: Just like all of the DVDs I've purchased on General MacArthur, WWII is glossed over except for the Philippines.  I was looking forward to the time between leaving the Philippines and returning to the Philippines.  MacArthur was a genius, but how did he apply it to the island hopping campaign?
This is an accurate biography of General Douglas Mac Arthur. The resourses used are creditable and accurate. Great story about a Great American.
